column5: MICT Even with an order of 13M the sp is down today Seems that shareholders who have tendered are hoping the deal with BNN comes through but remaining shares dont seem to be in demand so just the brief pop on the news and right back down Might indicate that there is no confidence among investors that the BNN deal will come through otherwise there would be a line for these seemingly discounted shares My guess is that tender is cancelled jmo Disclaimer I hold only 300 shares and not tendered
